    <item>
      <title>允许 PE 所有权对 NFL 大有裨益：Velocity 的 Abrams</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-27/allowing-pe-ownership-is-great-for-nfl-velocity-s-abrams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NFL 放宽了职业体育中最严格的所有权规定，允许私募股权持有一支球队 10% 的股份。Velocity Capital Management 创始合伙人 David Abrams 在“Bloomberg The Close”节目中表示，这一决定对 NFL 来说意义重大，早就应该宣布了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-27/allowing-pe-ownership-is-great-for-nfl-velocity-s-abrams</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国企业 DEI 业务陷入低迷：Ariel Investments 的 Patrick</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-27/corporate-america-seeing-slump-in-dei-ariel-investments-patrick</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究表明，美国财富 500 强企业继续优先考虑多样性、公平性和包容性。然而，同一项研究还表明，在更广泛的公司中，有色人种董事的数量有所下降。Ariel Investments 首席传播官 Ariel Patrick 将分享这项研究的见解。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-27/corporate-america-seeing-slump-in-dei-ariel-investments-patrick</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 21:15:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NFL 允许私募股权入股，开启新时代</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nfl-owners-set-to-vote-on-letting-private-equity-invest-in-teams</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国职业橄榄球大联盟 (NFL) 球队老板投票允许私募股权公司收购其球队的股份，此举预计将吸引数十亿美元的新资本，同时提高已经飙升的球队估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/nfl-owners-set-to-vote-on-letting-private-equity-invest-in-teams</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 13:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>动能指标显示东南亚货币上涨面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/momentum-gauge-signals-risk-to-southeast-asian-currency-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[至少一项备受关注的动能指标显示，随着投资者对美联储即将调整政策的热情消退，东南亚货币兑美元的强劲涨势可能失去动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/momentum-gauge-signals-risk-to-southeast-asian-currency-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 07:11:56 GMT</pubDate>
